Back in the day, there was nothing more fun for kids than spending hours outside. These days, there are a lot of exciting options for kids inside: iPads, smartphones, the list (unfortunately) goes on. If you’re hoping to get your kids off their screens and into the great outdoors, sprucing up your backyard with the right equipment can go a long way. From trampolines to splash pads, here’s everything you need to turn your backyard into a wonderland for kids. HuffPost receives a share from retailers on this page. Every item is independently selected by the HuffPost Shopping team. Prices and availability are subject to change.